     <p>But that's not all! The extended Wild feature is where things really get interesting. First, you need to collect nitro vials to unlock this feature. Once you've collected enough, you can trigger the extended Wild, which can cover all reels. This means you'll have a much better chance of hitting those big payouts. Just be careful not to get too caught up in the action and forget to enjoy the experience!</p>

     <p>Overall, the special features in Cave of Fortune are some of the most exciting and innovative we've seen in a long time. Whether you're a veteran slots player or a newbie just getting into the game, you're sure to love the wild ride that this game has in store for you. So grab your pickaxe, put on your helmet and get ready to explore the Cave of Fortune! Who knows, maybe you'll strike it rich.</p>"
